CEREGE Calibration Curve (NaI)

data(AIX_NaI_curve)

Format

An object of class CalibrationCurve.

LaboratoryCEREGE
InstrumentCanberra Inspector 1000
DetectorNaI
AuthorsCEREGE Luminescence Team

AIX_NaI_data
